\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\qc\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf1 ACT 3}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 INT. DESTROYED REMAINS OF THE CARGO HOLD}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The room is a burning pile of twisted metal and plastic. The roof has been mostly torn off and the far wall is vertically split in the center all the way down to the floor. Water is trickling in and starting to pool near Aaron's head. Aaron suddenly jolts awake. His head is bleeding and there are scorch marks on his clothes, but he seems otherwise in-tact.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He quickly checks himself out and then begins to search for the Woman. She is laying crushed under one of the crates. Aaron can see her arm and shoulder just above the rising water line. He rushes over to her to see if she's still alive. He lifts her head and can see her eyes are fixed, unblinking. }
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron desperately pushes his shoulder into the crate to see if he can free her, but it doesn't move. He holds her head in his hands for a moment and notices a pendant on a chain around her neck. He lifts it out of the water and sees that it has an inscription, "For Callie." He gently pulls off the necklace and lets her sink back into the rising water.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'm so sorry Callie.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 EXT. THE ICE FIELDS - DUSK}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron climbs out of the wreckage and into the snowy hillside. Once over the ridge he can see it's not a hillside at all, but an impact crater. Whatever crashed here has made bowl in the ice nearly 100 yards across in an otherwise flat plane of ice and snow. The surrounding burning debris is melting the snow causing the center to fill with water. Soon the remains of the cargo hold that brought him here will be completely submerged. The surrounding landscape is a bleak white endless plane of ice and snow, now barely visible as the last of the daylight fades.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron notices that despite the time of day, there isn't a sunset. He looks up at the dimming sun in the center of the sky to see why it's so dark out. As he watches it gets even darker. He mutters to himself as it completely fades and ultimately disappears. This is not a solar eclipse, the sun has simply gone out.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Well shit. I guess eventually there has to be a point where it actually can't get any worse.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 EXT. THE ICE FIELDS - NIGHT}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 In the darkness he can now make out a distant light source. Without any other points of interest on the horizon, he begins walking. The snow crunches under his simple prison-issue shoes. He can see the light getting closer, but almost nothing else. There is no moonlight, and the dim starlight only hugs the edges of the horizon. The sky is completely black. The only light he can make out comes from some distant city over the horizon, and a smaller light source from what must be a building a few miles away.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 EXT. OUTSIDE THE ICE RACER BAR - NIGHT}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The bar is a welcome site against the harsh frozen landscape. It's a well lit 2 story building with smoke rising from the chimney. Aaron can hear laughter and music coming from within. Multiple complicated looking vehicles are half-hazardly parked outside. }
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 INT. ICE RACER BAR - NIGHT}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Inside the bar men and women are eating and drinking at tables scattered throughout the room. They are wearing heavy snow gear, with open jackets and padded pants. A long bar on the far wall has multiple people eating and discussing technical specs of snow machines.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 People take notice as Aaron walks into the room. His shaved head and lightweight clothing make him look more than different from everyone else here. Once he's noticed, people end their conversations and stare. Soon the entire room is quiet and watching him. One of the workers behind the bar begins pressing buttons on a wall panel.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'm sorry, did I do something wrong?}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 A huge man with a pistol in his hand stands up and aims the weapon at Aaron.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MAN WITH GUN}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You know the rules asshole, no Tourists! }
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron raises his hands and takes a step back.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'm not a Tourist, I'm lost!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MAN WITH GUN}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Then we should send you back where you came from, yeah?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I honestly don't know if that's even an option any more...}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MAN WITH GUN}
\par\pard\plain \li2880\ri2160\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 (laughs) }
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Oh yeah, that's an option.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  }
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 A metal pipe strikes Aaron in the back of the head and he falls forward. Before he can even try to get up, a chair smashes down on his back and a heavy boot kicks him in the side of the head. }
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 EXT. OUTSIDE THE ICE RACER BAR - NIGHT}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron is dragged out of the bar into the area being used as a parking lot. In the center of the lot is a large metal post with a light on top. Aaron is beaten with pipes and chains as they drag him to the base of the post.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Stop, please stop! I didn't do anything!}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The crowd ignores his pleas and wrap the chain around him, tying him to the post. They finally back away as the large man who previously had the gun now approaches with what looks like a gas can. He stops short of pouring the gas when he sees blue and red flashing lights approaching through the darkness. }
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Two hover bikes glide up to the bar with their police lights on and burst the siren a few short squawks. }
