\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'm not a Tourist! I don't even know what you're talking about! Nobody was rebuilt, the thing crashed and I walked here! That's it!}
