\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You're being rebuilt right now, you idiot. I can see you rebuilding!}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Bike Cop 1 points his gun back down at Aaron's leg. The bullet hole is already closing. }
